@startuml Voice Interaction Sequence
' Simplified Voice Input and Audio Generation Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend" as API
participant "Voice Processing" as Voice
participant "Audio Generation" as Audio
participant "File System" as FS

User -> FE: Click microphone & speak
FE -> API: Voice input request
API -> Voice: Process speech
Voice -> API: Transcribed text
API -> API: Generate story from voice

API -> Audio: Create narration
Audio -> Audio: Process story text
Audio -> FS: Save audio files
Audio -> API: Audio file paths

API -> FE: Story with audio
FE -> User: Display story + audio controls

User -> FE: Play audio
FE -> FS: Load audio
FS -> FE: Audio data
FE -> User: Play narration

@enduml
